@zelleran, [Angel of Jubilation](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Angel of Jubilation) will make it even worse if this guy is on the other side of the board. Since angel prevents you from sacrificing **CREATURES** and this guys forces opponent to sacrifice **PERMANENTS**, you'll have no choice but to sacrifice your artifacts, lands or even Planeswalkers.  
Right choice would be [Sigarda](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sigarda).  

@kaleidostorm, you only sacrifice one because it only dealt one damage.
